{"tid":464161,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［重點偷跑］FIFA以後唔出實體碟 變付費下載！","createTime":"2017-11-10T09:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T11:05:07.000Z","uid":13385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bb8db4e783c6bb1c829260cff8714be059844c","tid":464161,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"每當新版的《FIFA》推出，足球迷就會立即買實體遊戲碟滿足一下。不過，Electronic Arts總裁 Andrew Wilson表示網上付費訂閱或更新，將取代「一年一碟」的傳統，堅持年年買實體碟的球迷，這份執著要「被消失」了。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報道，EA總裁 Andrew Wilson指遊戲漸漸由發售實體光碟，轉移至網上付費下載整個新遊戲，包括購買裝備或球員名單等，所以《FIFA 18》和《Madden》的遊戲出版商將考慮，停止發售每年新版的遊戲實體碟。<br />\n<br />\nAndrew Wilson說隨著銷售模式數碼化，串流服務等變得更實用。不過，他並沒有透露正式停止的時間表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171110/57441104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171110%2F57441104&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5a099dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171110%2F57441104&h=9e42636f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171110/57441104</a><br />\n<br />\n想草下碟都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55e8e7c4fda69b5b9128da85a16377f59ed5cce","tid":464161,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"迫人買官方early access"},{"pid":"91c7a41dc6e837feaf4a5104902987c15ca521a1","tid":464161,"uid":115042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:09:31.000Z","msg":"數碼版都好,一年一隻想儲碟都未必有位<br />\n<br />\n係唔想D COINS,UT TEAM班人<br />\n每年都清空同要辟掉重練"},{"pid":"54ac2ef5bbe6fbfd543bfc92df3527c4550477a3","tid":464161,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"此回